{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5efe8c9a5f","title":"整个华北工作应以游击战争为唯一方向","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0826a7d041","index":0,"year":1937,"month":9,"day":25,"articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji2.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"7b5eb48853","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据中央档案馆保存的抄件刊印。"},{"id":"11474d8f5c","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":1,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"218f47079e","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":1,"offset":11,"text":"胡服，即刘少奇。尚昆，即杨尚昆，一九○七年生，四川潼南人，当时任中共中央北方局副书记。朱瑞（一九○五——一九四八），江苏宿迁人，当时任中共中央北方局军委书记。"},{"id":"e326469132","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":1,"offset":18,"text":"朱，指朱德。彭，指彭德怀，当时任八路军副总司令。任，指任弼时，当时任八路军政治部主任。"},{"id":"c8f51e7544","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":4,"part_index":3,"offset":93,"text":"冯治安（一八九六——一九五四），河北故城人，当时任国民党军第一集团军副总司令兼第七十七军军长。黄绍竑（一八九五——一九六六），广西容县人，当时任国民党政府军事委员会第一部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8a38135652","type":"title","text":"整个华北工作应以游击战争为唯一方向","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11474d8f5c","type":"paragraph","text":"周并转胡服、尚昆、朱瑞并告朱、彭、任：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"218f47079e","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、整个华北工作，应以游击战争为唯一方向。一切工作，例如民运、统一战线等等，应环绕于游击战争。华北正规战如失败，我们不负责任；但游击战争如失败，我们须负严重的责任。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e326469132","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、除山西部署已告外，应令河北党注全力于游击战争，借着红军抗战的声威，发动全华北党（包括山东在内）动员群众，收编散兵散枪，普遍地但是有计划地组成游击队。为此目的，周是否应与冯治安、黄绍竑等再谈一次，请酌。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8f51e7544","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、为此目的，应着重于高级干部之分配及独立领导的党政军集体机关之组织。要设想在敌整个占领华北后，我们能坚持广泛有力的游击战争。要告诉全党（要发动党内党外），今后没有别的工作，唯一的就是游击战争。为此目的，红军应给予一切可能的助力。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c9ec37fda","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、请以整个华北的部署见告。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4edf436c79","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebd6a64dec","type":"paragraph","text":"二十五日","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"5efe8c9a5f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":37,"end":36}}}},"__N_SSG":true}